###
# SELECTS THE EMACS KEYMAP
###
bindkey -e

###
# DEFINES THE CTRL-P BINDKEY
###
bindkey '^p' history-search-backward

###
# DEFINES THE CTRL-N BINDKEY
###
bindkey '^n' history-search-forward
